  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b89\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0baa\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbe\u0bb0\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bbe \u0b9a\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0ba4\u0bcd \u0ba4\u0b9f\u0bc8",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Prohibition to go near the Bandaranayak statue at Kalimugathidal",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Fort Justice Court has issued a restraining order against entering the 50-meter circle around the statue of Bandaranaike in the Kalimugattidal area.",
        "Colombo - The Fort Magistrate Court has issued a restraining order against the Kalimugattidal Kota Go Kama protestors from entering the 50 meter circle around the Bandaranaike statue there.",
        "Colombo Fort Magistrate Dilina Gamage has issued this order following a request made by the Fort Police that there is a possibility of damage to the statue."
      ],
